design_cases.name: Urban Drone Delivery System
design_cases.description: High-tech aerial delivery system for dense urban areas using autonomous drones. Optimized for small packages and rapid delivery in metropolitan regions with high-rise buildings. Uses rooftop hubs and AI-powered traffic management.

design_cases.name: Smart Locker Integration System
design_cases.description: Network of intelligent lockers at strategic locations (stations, malls, apartments) with 24/7 access. Uses predictive placement, temperature control for perishables, and mobile authentication.
